<br>
My original idea was to camp the Condensed Chunks of {Shadow, Ice, Fire}<br>
<br>
From the lack of mobs dropping these items in zones that are green to me [Twilight Sea and Shadoweavers] I might have to change that tactic...<br>
<br>
This is what I was thinking of doing.... Please feel free to let me know if there is a easier (cost efficient/time efficient) way to do it.<br>
<br>
Lockpicks - Triv 88<br>
Fier'Dal Fletching Kit - Triv 163<br>
Acrylia Armor or Black Acrylia Weapons to 200+<br>
<br>
from the research I have done there does not seem to be a cost effective/time effective way to raise smithing past 163 as a Wood Elf.<br>
<br>
Opinions are Welcome...<br>
<br>
Edit.......<br>
My STR is 170 when I buff myself with Strength of Earth. Wisdom is 103, Int 100. By Cost effective I mean between 5-10k to get to 200. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/btribalfury31319.showUserPublicProfile?gid=deladriendil>Deladriendil</A> at: 12/30/02 3:52:00 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/btribalfury31319.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solairs>Solairs</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 5:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ftribalfury31319frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Smithing 101</span><hr size=1> Del,<br>
