skill 225. Personal observations: GAAAAAAHHHHHh getting essence of wind is a pain in the $#@$!$#@!. To make the acrylia temper you need two windstones(put in mortar and pestle and crush em), one essence of wind and one vial of clear mana. Just making the tempers to do attempts is getting very costly and I dont have the time to farm cash much. Hope some of this info proves helpful<br>
